## Score [/score/{idScore}]
A single Score object with all its details

+ Parameters
    + idScore (required, string, `541eec44753a9500003e56c0`) ... String `idScore` of the Score to perform action with. Has example value.

+ Model (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    
    JSON representation of Score Resource.

    + Body
    
            {
                "_id": "841eec44753a9500003e56c0",
                "home": 0,
                "guest": 0,
                "owner": "117446425362491737929"
            }
    
### Retrieve a single Score [GET]
+ Response 200
    [Score][]

